Text: Esenjay Exploration Inc ESNJ Cc here are the details for the transaction completed on Thursday April Andrea Vail Reed contacted us with a potential bidder for the remaining shares of ESNJ held in the JEDI account Andrea relayed to us to sell the shares inline with the current market last trade was Andrea instructed Wayne Williams of Aspect Resources to contact us about a potential trade After receiving a call from Wayne we agreed to sell shares of ESNJ at a price of Any questions please call David Vitrella
